ji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe477c57bab75ff2155a0d6e6cd0cb37c750db1a","tid":877681,"uid":112720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T00:50:46.000Z","msg":"海富苑600萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁平有古怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔計<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cdec2a1793ba503efc8cb71dae83f0ef1d53e93","tid":877681,"uid":119996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"47f0b739ce913d0673b6a8e7760d633c3ec255db","tid":877681,"uid":28245,"like":88,"dislike":5,"score":83,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T14:10:21.000Z","msg":"其實知唔知點解居屋呢排跌得最快？<br />\n林鄭為新居屋封左頂 同市價脫勾<br />\n啟德 南昌一線地段只係$7500一尺左右<br />\n而市面上既優質居屋大部份都近20年樓齡<br />\n尺價過$10,000<br />\n<br />\n你可能會話新居屋好難抽，無錯，<br />\n但7:3既公營房屋供應底下 包括42折既綠置居<br />\n拎緊綠表班人唔會再同你爭2手居屋<br />\n換言之 你想賣樓 一年得2500個機會<br />\n而大部份呢班買家基於入息資產限制 <br />\n根本唔會負擔到過每尺過萬<br />\n重點係20年樓齡打後 銀行唔會做到25年 + 9成按<br />\n就算做到 9成按 加息對呢班業主黎講根本難以應付<br />\n<br />\n外加一堆經濟影響已經未計<br />\n<br />\n結論係 市面600萬以上既居屋好快會絕跡<br />\n一年內<br />\n市區居屋尺價會回落去7500-8500左右<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T00:52:04.000Z","msg":"嘩 不得了。。。"},{"pid":"8e58b82cf80c52e92e5792060ff1109a59b0345f","tid":877681,"uid":28245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T01:04:47.000Z","msg":"海富算係全港居屋王<br />\n640 尺都係6 球"},{"pid":"66eb37222f84fd319c5bfc5a0afdb570d249c60a","tid":877681,"uid":6297,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4cdec2a1793ba503efc8cb71dae83f0ef1d53e93","tid":877681,"uid":119996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"47f0b739ce913d0673b6a8e7760d633c3ec255db","tid":877681,"uid":28245,"like":88,"dislike":5,"score":83,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"